3. ZERO-POINT ENERGY AND AETHER CLAIM STRUCTURE

3.1 The Rebranding Loop

The Institute has identified a repeating historical cycle called the Perpetual Rebranding of Disproven Concepts (PRDC):

Old Term	New Term
Aether	Quantum vacuum
Perpetual motion	Over-unity
Free energy	Zero-point extraction
Anti-gravity	Exotic propulsion
Genius	Suppressed researcher
Rejected paper	Censored discovery

This process is known as Terminological Escape Velocity (TEV) — when a claim avoids criticism by changing vocabulary faster than it can be evaluated.

